         <ab>Y59.1 (mss. 5, 40, 88, 400, 410):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ēn gyāg zōt dast pad pādyāb kardan ud āb andar skūrag kardan <em>ahurəm mazdąm</em>.  ...</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At this passage. the <em>zōt</em> should wash his hands with <em>pādyāb</em> and pour water in the bowl (and continue with) <em>ahurəm mazdąm</em> ..."</ab>
